						<p>It says that a Chōṟaṉ Aṅgarāyaṉ of Perumpuli-ūr gifted 4 <hi rend="italic">mā</hi> of land to a <hi rend="italic">pāraśivaṉ</hi> called Mūṉṟukūṟṟu-vājya-mārāyaṉ.</p>						

